name: CampingPacker
0:
”Alexa, start Camping Packer”
”Alexa, ask Camping Packer to start a trip.”
”Alexa, ask Camping Packer to resume trip.”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: camping packer
des: Have you ever left for the great outdoors with that nagging feeling that you left something behind? Camping Packer suggests numerous items, one by one, while you pack, and gives you the freedom to mark each item as packed, skipped, or unneeded. Need a break? Exit and come back later; resume where you left off! Camping Packer can also ask you a few questions to narrow the list down to those items that you need, skipping those that you don't.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
